    <item>
      <title>英超联赛面临英国政府前所未有的监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/premier-league-faces-unprecedented-regulation-from-uk-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新的足球监管机构将有权决定利润丰厚的英格兰足球超级联赛如何向较小的俱乐部分配资金，从而使该监管机构对该国最受欢迎的运动拥有更大的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/premier-league-faces-unprecedented-regulation-from-uk-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
