      <title>科技股尾盘上涨，特斯拉涨幅达 9%：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司以稳健的业绩拉开了“七巨头”财报季的序幕，大型科技股在尾盘上涨。债券收益率因市场押注美联储将采取谨慎降息方式而上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 22:29:48 GMT</pubDate>
